universum.studios.android.setting.key

Class SimplePreferenceKeyModificator

  • java.lang.Object
    • universum.studios.android.setting.key.SimplePreferenceKeyModificator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PreferenceKeyModificator

    public class SimplePreferenceKeyModificator
extends Object
implements PreferenceKeyModificator
    A simple implementation of PreferenceKeyModificator that uses KeyModificator supplied to SimplePreferenceKeyModificator(KeyModificator) constructor to perform modification of key for any preference passed to modifyKey(Preference).
    Author:
    Martin Albedinsky
